Of course.

447
00:38:27,222 --> 00:38:30,975
所以我确定不是自己解码的。
So I made sure that it was not by decoding it myself.

448
00:38:32,185 --> 00:38:39,150
如你所见，报告只说江青号的速度和航线没有改变。
As you see, it reports only that the kiang ching has made no change in speed or course.

449
00:38:39,234 --> 00:38:41,402
我知道那不重要。
I knew that was of no importance.

450
00:38:41,486 --> 00:38:51,371
教授，你有没有想过我可能会把这门课…你耽误了我们大约两个小时!
Professor, did it ever occur to you that I might be steering a course to be... You've lost us approximately two hours!

451
00:38:51,454 --> 00:38:54,040
我很抱歉，队长。
I'm very sorry, captain.

452
00:38:54,123 --> 00:38:57,293
-我想我学到了一些东西。-我希望如此。
- And I think I have learned something. - I hope so.

453
00:39:11,099 --> 00:39:14,727
如果你想偷听谈话，就用对讲机。这是更容易。
If you want to listen in on conversations, use the intercom. It's easier.

454
00:39:14,811 --> 00:39:17,188
我不希望听到这段对话。
That conversation I would prefer not to have heard.

455
00:39:17,272 --> 00:39:20,608
-但我在等着见你。-好吧，你看我。我很忙。
- But I was waiting to see you. - Okay, you see me. I'm busy.

456
00:39:20,692 --> 00:39:27,907
我和蒙泰尔教授共事多年了，但我从来没有听过有人像您这样对他这个领域里最伟大的科学家说话。
Many years have I been with professor montel, but never before have I heard anyone speak like you to the greatest scientist in his field.

457
00:39:27,991 --> 00:39:31,786
蒙泰尔教授的领域不是指挥一艘古怪的潜艇。我的是。
Professor montel's field isn't commanding a screwball submarine. Mine is.

458
00:39:31,870 --> 00:39:36,958
如果有必要这么无礼的话，我希望这次旅行时间很短。
If such rudeness is necessary, I hope this will be a very short cruise.

459
00:39:38,960 --> 00:39:42,297
你找我有什么事?
What'd you want to see me about?

460
00:39:51,514 --> 00:39:53,433
——Joto。——是的,先生?
- Joto. - Yes, sir?

461
00:39:53,516 --> 00:39:59,272
将来，当一条消息传到这艘船上时，不管谁说这是不必要的，我都会收到，你明白吗?
In the future, when a message comes in to this boat, I get it, no matter who says it's unnecessary, you understand?

462
00:39:59,355 --> 00:40:01,274
是的,先生。
Yes, sir.

463
00:40:01,357 --> 00:40:05,028
Oh-oh-oh-oh-oh !
Oh-oh-oh-oh-oh!

464
00:40:08,573 --> 00:40:10,783
不，不，不。
No, no, no, no.

465
00:40:10,867 --> 00:40:13,244
这一次，他是对的。
This time, he was right.

466
00:40:33,473 --> 00:40:37,101
我们可以从桥上走吗?
May we come on the bridge?

467
00:40:37,185 --> 00:40:39,187
确定。帮助你自己。
Sure. Help yourself.

468
00:40:40,980 --> 00:40:43,274
联络飞机正按计划接近!
Contact plane approaching on schedule!

469
00:40:43,358 --> 00:40:45,276
不够好。
Good enough.

470
00:40:49,447 --> 00:40:51,366
好吧,查理。
Okay, Charlie.

471
00:40:58,790 --> 00:41:01,084
在这里!
There it is!

472
00:41:20,561 --> 00:41:22,522
这个是给你的，医生。
Well, this one's for you, doc.

473
00:41:22,605 --> 00:41:27,568
"情报报告江庆携带非传统61-j太空舱"
“Intelligence reports kiang ching carrying unconventional-type 61-j capsule.”

474
00:41:27,652 --> 00:41:31,531
藤森签署。”“61-j太空舱是什么?”
Signed, “fujimori.” what's a 61-j capsule?

475
00:41:31,614 --> 00:41:33,574
引爆原子弹的炸药
The charge to explode an a-bomb.

476
00:41:33,658 --> 00:41:39,414
嗨,队长。雷达显示有物体接近，方位355度。
Hey, skipper. Radar shows surface object approaching, bearing 355 degrees.

477
00:41:39,497 --> 00:41:42,417
——速度?-还不知道，但他在快速接近。
- Speed? - Can't tell yet, but he's closing fast.

478
00:41:42,500 --> 00:41:45,211
——范围。- 3800码。
- Range. - 3,800 yards.

479
00:41:45,294 --> 00:41:48,089
也许那艘货船看到了我们的信号，来追我们了。
Maybe the freighter has seen our signal and comes after us.

480
00:41:48,172 --> 00:41:49,172
钻井平台为红色。
Rig for red.

481
00:42:18,995 --> 00:42:21,039
一艘潜艇在追我们。
A sub's after us.

482
00:42:21,122 --> 00:42:24,459
子吗?我以为这是科学考察。
A sub? I thought this was a scientific expedition.

483
00:42:24,542 --> 00:42:26,586
是的，我们要谨慎行事。
It is, and we're gonna play it safe.

484
00:42:26,669 --> 00:42:30,006
除非万不得已，否则流鼻血也没用。
No use getting a bloody nose unless we have to.

485
00:42:32,175 --> 00:42:34,635
她在水下听我们说话。
She's submerged and listening for us.

486
00:42:34,719 --> 00:42:38,097
-所以她才不再联系我-什么意思?
- That's why she stopped pinging. - What does this mean?

487
00:42:38,181 --> 00:42:42,643
意思是她在保存鱼雷，等我们浮出水面。
It means she's saving her torpedoes, waiting till we surface.

488
00:42:42,727 --> 00:42:47,732
再过一天，博士，我们就能把鱼雷发射管彻底检修完。
Just one more day, doc, and we'd have finished overhauling those torpedo tubes.

489
00:42:47,815 --> 00:42:49,984
你能看到她的瞄准镜吗?
Can you see her scope?

490
00:42:52,445 --> 00:42:54,447
我们也可以装死。
Well, we can play possum too.

491
00:42:55,740 --> 00:42:59,285
-氢怎么样了?-增加到3%。
- How's the hydrogen? - Built up to three percent.

492
00:43:01,245 --> 00:43:04,248
我们不能冒险在这里浮出水面。我们得跑了。
Well, we can't chance surfacing here. We've got to make a run for it.

493
00:43:04,332 --> 00:43:07,752
教授，我觉得你们俩最好都待在自己的房间里。
Professor, I think you'd both better stay in your quarters.

494
00:43:07,835 --> 00:43:09,754
范围。
Down scope.

495
00:43:28,523 --> 00:43:31,025
他们还在船尾，船长。
They're still on our stern, skipper.

496
00:43:43,996 --> 00:43:47,834
-氢气怎么样?-按我们的百分比计算，还在增加。
- How's that hydrogen gas? - F our percent and still building.

497
00:43:57,468 --> 00:44:00,805
带她了!
Take her up!

498
00:44:09,647 --> 00:44:11,566
好吧,查理。
Okay, Charlie.

499
00:44:40,344 --> 00:44:42,638
你最好离桥远点，教授。
You better keep off the bridge, professor.

500
00:44:42,722 --> 00:44:44,640
我不上去。
I'm not going up.

501
00:44:44,724 --> 00:44:49,562
如果船长发现你在控制室，他会大发雷霆的。
The skipper'd blow his top if he even found you here in the control room.

502
00:44:49,645 --> 00:44:52,648
-请坐，教授。抓住一些空气。——谢谢。
- Sit down, professor. Grab some air. - Thank you.

503
00:44:55,193 --> 00:44:57,778
你认出潜水艇了吗?
Have you identified the submarine?

504
00:44:57,862 --> 00:45:00,489
不。我们还没见过她呢。
No. We haven't even seen her yet.

505
00:45:00,573 --> 00:45:03,367
他们在上面试图发现她。
They're topside trying to spot her now.

506
00:45:03,451 --> 00:45:06,204
还没找到她，船长。
No sign of her yet, skipper.

507
00:45:06,287 --> 00:45:09,415
声纳显示她就在附近。通知炮手。
Sonar tells us she's not far. Alert the gun crew.

508
00:45:09,498 --> 00:45:12,460
——什么?——我知道。我们不是在找麻烦。
- What? - I know. We're not lookin' for trouble.

509
00:45:12,543 --> 00:45:16,088
但不保护自己才是傻瓜。
But we'd be fools not to protect ourselves.

510
00:45:16,172 --> 00:45:18,090
准备战斗!
Alert for battle stations!

511
00:45:18,174 --> 00:45:21,219
炮手准备上甲板炮。
Gun crew stand by to man the deck gun.

512
00:45:23,971 --> 00:45:25,973
那些鱼雷呢?
What about these torpedoes?

513
00:45:27,475 --> 00:45:31,312
你知道那些管子还没检查过。忘记了鱼雷!
You know those tubes haven't been checked. Forget the torpedoes!

514
00:45:31,395 --> 00:45:34,523
-她现在在哪里，joto?-范围,1500。
- Where is she now, joto? - Range, 1,500.

515
00:45:34,607 --> 00:45:37,068
她要么搬出去，要么就会浮出水面。
Either she's moving out, or she's gonna surface.

516
00:45:40,154 --> 00:45:41,781
她来了，船长!
There she is, skipper!

517
00:45:45,701 --> 00:45:47,620
他们在甲板上。
They're coming out on deck.

518
00:45:47,703 --> 00:45:49,664
问他们我们在哪，查理。
Ask them where we are, Charlie.

519
00:45:49,747 --> 00:45:51,999
-为什么不现在就上5英寸的?——不!
- Why not man the five-incher now? - No!

520
00:45:52,083 --> 00:45:56,087
一旦他们发现枪旁有船员，就会向我们发射鱼雷。
The minute they spot a crew near that gun, they'll throw torpedoes at us.

521
00:46:01,259 --> 00:46:02,260
他们在说什么?
What are they saying?

522
00:46:02,343 --> 00:46:05,012
他们想知道我们是谁，我们在这里干什么。
They want to know who we are and what we're doing here.

523
00:46:05,096 --> 00:46:09,183
告诉他们我们是去北极的私人科学探险队。
Tell 'em we're a private scientific expedition headed for the arctic.

524
00:46:15,022 --> 00:46:17,692
他们坚持要登船。
They insist on boarding us.

525
00:46:17,775 --> 00:46:20,236
嗯,保持总得”。告诉他们我们不明白。
Well, keep stallin'. Tell 'em we don't understand.

526
00:46:20,319 --> 00:46:22,738
请他们重复留言。
Ask them to repeat the message.

527
00:46:35,126 --> 00:46:38,671
在船头放一个。让他们重复一遍，查理。
Put one over our bow. Keep asking them to repeat, Charlie.

528
00:46:41,382 --> 00:46:45,011
把我们的鼻子转向她。带领001人。
Turn our nose into her. Steer 001.

529
00:46:45,094 --> 00:46:48,055
准备好拿起枪。
And get ready to man that gun.

530
00:47:05,323 --> 00:47:08,075
不要靠近救生索!
Keep clear of the lifeline!

531
00:47:16,625 --> 00:47:18,627
右满舵。
Right full rudder.

532
00:47:51,869 --> 00:47:53,746
鱼雷!
Torpedo!

533
00:47:57,124 --> 00:47:59,043
清除甲板!清除甲板!
Clear the deck! Clear the deck!

534
00:47:59,126 --> 00:48:00,920
潜水!
Dive!

535
00:48:18,104 --> 00:48:20,106
关闭舱口!
Close the hatch!

536
00:48:27,655 --> 00:48:30,157
我的手!我的手!
My hand! My hand!

537
00:48:31,617 --> 00:48:34,120
我的手!
My hand!

538
00:48:34,203 --> 00:48:38,290
-给我一把刀!——不!不!不!
- Give me a knife! - No! No! No!

539
00:48:40,584 --> 00:48:44,088
在这里。
Here.

540
00:48:50,928 --> 00:48:53,180
-他怎么样了?他是如何?-是他的拇指。
- How is he? How is he? - It's his thumb.

541
00:48:55,766 --> 00:48:57,726
好吧。把他们都抓下来。
All right. Get 'em all below.

542
00:48:57,810 --> 00:48:59,937
嘿,你们!快上来!帮我一把，快!
Hey, you guys! Come on up here! Give me a hand, quick!

543
00:49:01,188 --> 00:49:03,023
我们装运的水太多了。拖不住她了。
We ship too much water. Can't hold her up.

544
00:49:03,107 --> 00:49:05,107
把角度移开，让它沉到水底。
Get the angle off and let her settle to the bottom.

545
00:49:05,151 --> 00:49:06,986
所有回满。
All back full.

546
00:49:19,165 --> 00:49:21,667
敌人的鱼雷发射。
Enemy torpedo fired.

547
00:49:27,173 --> 00:49:30,759
二号鱼从篮子里出来。
Number two fish out of their basket.

548
00:49:57,328 --> 00:49:59,788
固定所有运转的机器。保持沉默。
Secure all running machinery. Remain silent.

549
00:49:59,872 --> 00:50:02,041
舱底泵马达失灵，船长。
Bilge pump motor's fioodeo', skipper.

550
00:50:02,124 --> 00:50:04,668
排成一排。把水倒进机舱的舱底。
Form a bucket line. Dump the water in the engine room bilges.

551
00:50:04,752 --> 00:50:08,839
那个浴缸是为我们准备的，船长。她已经很接近了。
That tub's laying for us, skipper. She's coming real close.

552
00:50:50,381 --> 00:50:52,007
我失去了她。
I lost her.

553
00:50:52,925 --> 00:50:55,219
她现在什么都没说。没有声音。
Nothing out of her now. No sound.

554
00:50:58,556 --> 00:51:01,016
你觉得呢，船长?
What do you think, skipper?

555
00:51:01,100 --> 00:51:04,436
我觉得她跟我们耍的把戏一样。
I think she's pulling the same trick we are.

556
00:51:21,996 --> 00:51:26,000
现在注意那海水。我们不希望船上有氯气。
Now watch that salt water. We don't want any chlorine gas in the boat.

557
00:51:39,054 --> 00:51:40,973
持有它。
Hold it.

558
00:51:42,057 --> 00:51:45,019
队长，这高温快把我们累死了。
Captain, this hot heat is killing us.

559
00:51:45,102 --> 00:51:47,021
我们得把电扇打开。
We got to turn on the fans.

560
00:51:47,104 --> 00:51:51,900
如果他们听到了我们的粉丝的声音，你就不用担心热死了，孩子。
If they heard our fans, you wouldn't have to worry about the heat killing you, boy.

561
00:51:51,984 --> 00:51:55,070
好吧，我马上给你补充情况。
All right, I'll fill in the picture for you quick.

562
00:51:55,154 --> 00:51:58,699
我们有鱼雷，但发射管无法发射。
We got torpedoes, but our tubes aren't in condition to fire 'em.

563
00:51:58,782 --> 00:52:03,621
红色潜艇和我们一样停在海底，等着声纳发现我们。
And the red sub's parked on the bottom like we are, waitin' to pick us up on sonar.

564
00:52:03,704 --> 00:52:06,707
一旦她这么做了，她会朝我们扔更多的鱼。
Once she does, she'll throw more fish at us.

565
00:52:06,790 --> 00:52:11,754
所以问题是谁在没有空气的情况下能坚持得更久……是红色的还是我们。
So it's a question of who can hold out longer without air... the reds or us.

566
00:52:11,837 --> 00:52:16,592
如果我们先突破，很有可能是最后一次突破。
If we break first, chances are it'll be our last break.

567
00:52:17,885 --> 00:52:21,055
我们还装载了氢。
And we're loaded with hydrogen.

568
00:52:21,138 --> 00:52:23,641
我们容易爆炸。
We're liable to explode.

569
00:52:23,724 --> 00:52:26,393
但有一件事对我们有利。
But we got one thing in our favor.

570
00:52:26,477 --> 00:52:29,271
我们可以通过闭上嘴来节省氧气。
We can save oxygen by shutting up.

571
00:52:31,148 --> 00:52:32,566
这是所有。
That's all.

572
00:53:24,410 --> 00:53:26,370
的,是吧?
Nothin', huh?

573
00:53:27,371 --> 00:53:29,289
一文不值。
Nothin'.

574
00:53:34,628 --> 00:53:36,630
我们得节省果汁。
We gotta save juice.

575
00:53:40,384 --> 00:53:42,636
转移到红色。
Shift to red.

576
00:53:47,224 --> 00:53:49,351
把耳朵竖起来，斯基。
Keep your ears open, ski.

577
00:55:14,728 --> 00:55:18,899
很抱歉，队长，我太蠢了。
I am sorry, captain, for being so stupid.

578
00:55:18,982 --> 00:55:21,443
没关系。别白费口舌了。
That's all right. Save your breath.

579
00:55:21,527 --> 00:55:23,529
你必须用那把刀。
You had to use the knife.

580
00:55:24,822 --> 00:55:29,284
如果你不关上舱门，我们都死了。
If you didn't close the hatch, we would all be dead.

581
00:55:31,495 --> 00:55:33,539
你击败。
You're beat.

582
00:55:33,622 --> 00:55:37,543
你最好回你的床上去，放松点。来吧。
You better get back to your bunk and take it easy. Come on.

583
00:56:50,741 --> 00:56:53,535
-我想告诉你怎么…——嘘。
- I want to tell you how... - Shh.

584
00:56:53,619 --> 00:56:55,621
不要说话。
Don't talk.

585
00:57:31,031 --> 00:57:33,033
队长。
Skipper.

586
00:57:35,285 --> 00:57:37,454
他的情况很糟糕。
He's in a bad way.

587
00:57:37,537 --> 00:57:42,084
我以为注射麻醉药能起作用，但他休克了，还失血过多。
I thought that hypo was gonna do the trick, but he's sufferin' from shock and loss of blood.

588
00:57:45,045 --> 00:57:49,508
如果他不马上呼吸点新鲜空气，你就只有一个教授了。
If he don't get some air right away, you're gonna have only one professor for cargo.

589
00:57:56,431 --> 00:58:00,352
那张床上有5万美金。
There's 50 grand in that bunk.

590
00:58:00,435 --> 00:58:03,480
五万块值一点空气。
Fifty grand is worth a little air.

591
00:58:07,776 --> 00:58:09,987
乔托，把白灯打开。
Joto, turn on the white lights.

592
00:58:25,794 --> 00:58:29,381
伙计们，我要试一试。
Boys, I'm gonna try a long shot.

593
00:58:29,464 --> 00:58:33,218
如果前几颗鱼雷打偏了，我们还有机会。
If her first couple of torpedoes miss us, we got a chance.

594
00:58:33,301 --> 00:58:38,056
我宁愿在没有空气的情况下昏倒，也不愿被鱼雷击中。
I'd rather pass out without air than have a torpedo come plowing through us.

595
00:58:41,018 --> 00:58:45,355
当我们启动水泵时，很容易产生火花。
Now when we start the pump, we're liable to get a spark.

596
00:58:46,898 --> 00:58:50,444
可能会燃烧掉氢，也可能不会。
Maybe it'll burn off the hydrogen, maybe it won't.

597
00:58:50,527 --> 00:58:56,658
如果不行，我们就会迅速爆炸，你永远感觉不到。
If it doesn't, we'll blow up so fast you'll never feel it.

598
00:58:58,910 --> 00:59:01,204
祝我们大家好运。
Good luck to all of us.

599
00:59:17,512 --> 00:59:20,140
-你都准备好了吗?——是的,先生。
- You got everything straight? - Yes, sir.

600
00:59:35,572 --> 00:59:38,909
现在我们来看看我们的生活是否正确。
Now here's where we find out if we've lived right.

601
01:00:13,944 --> 01:00:16,029
没有爆炸的可能。把消息传下去。
No more chance of explosion. Pass the word along.

602
01:00:16,113 --> 01:00:18,031
慢慢地转弯。
And build up the turns slowly.

603
01:00:18,115 --> 01:00:20,093
-别出声。——是的,先生。
