那些菲律宾游击队被隔绝和包围了。
Those philippine guerrillas were cut off and surrounded.

756
01:21:36,558 --> 01:21:38,644
他们必须有弹药和补给。
They had to have ammunition and supplies.

757
01:21:38,727 --> 01:21:41,772
我不能坐在我的罐子上让他们死。
I couldn't just sit there on my can and let 'em die.

758
01:21:41,855 --> 01:21:47,152
我知道水已经被挖空了，但我想我可以毫发无损地进出。
I knew the waters were mined, but I figured I could get in, get out without a scratch.

759
01:21:47,236 --> 01:21:49,238
所以我写了自己的命令。
So I wrote my own orders.

760
01:21:50,781 --> 01:21:54,410
我失去了潜艇和26个人。
I lost my sub and 26 men.

761
01:21:56,203 --> 01:21:58,664
如果!必须的，我还会再做一次。
And if! Had to, I'd do it again.

762
01:22:19,643 --> 01:22:24,273
我很抱歉……非常抱歉。
I'm sorry... Very sorry.

763
01:22:25,607 --> 01:22:28,318
我提这事都是不对的。
It was wrong of me even to mention it.

764
01:22:29,778 --> 01:22:32,072
算了吧。一切都结束了。
Forget it. It's all over.

765
01:22:42,791 --> 01:22:45,210
-你还好吧?——好。
- You all right? - Fine.

766
01:22:49,923 --> 01:22:56,180
这一切结束后，如果我们回来了，你怎么了?
When this is over, if we get back, what gives with you?

767
01:22:56,263 --> 01:23:00,767
——给了吗?-我是说，你打算怎么办?
- Gives? - I mean, what are you gonna do?

768
01:23:00,851 --> 01:23:03,729
我想是回巴黎吧?
Go back to Paris, I suppose, huh?

769
01:23:03,812 --> 01:23:06,106
-巴黎是我的家。-是的。
- Paris is my home. - Yeah.

770
01:23:08,484 --> 01:23:10,402
你呢?
And you?

771
01:23:10,486 --> 01:23:13,489
这一切结束后，你会怎样?
When this is over, what gives with you?

772
01:23:13,572 --> 01:23:15,491
我不知道。
I don't know.

773
01:23:18,202 --> 01:23:20,746
你去过巴黎吗?
Have you ever been in Paris?

774
01:23:20,829 --> 01:23:22,831
不,从来没有。
No, never.

775
01:23:23,999 --> 01:23:26,460
你会喜欢的。
You would love it.

776
01:23:26,543 --> 01:23:28,837
美国人总是这样。
Americans always do.

777
01:23:36,178 --> 01:23:38,680
我们不能待在这里。
Well, we can't stay here.

778
01:23:38,764 --> 01:23:41,892
如果他们把我们拖到早上，我们可能就回不去了。
If they hold us up till morning, we might never get back.

779
01:23:43,268 --> 01:23:46,396
我去看看有没有别的路出去。来吧。
I'm gonna see if there's another way out of here. Come on.

780
01:23:53,946 --> 01:23:56,490
你呆在这里。我马上回来。
You stay here. I'll be right back.

781
01:24:03,705 --> 01:24:05,624
在这里。
Here.

782
01:24:05,707 --> 01:24:09,253
你不需要这个，但有时看到它是一种安慰。
You won't need this, but sometimes the sight of it's a comfort.

783
01:24:09,336 --> 01:24:11,338
我马上就回来。
I'll be back in a minute.

784
01:25:09,521 --> 01:25:11,440
Lumfong !
Lumfong!

785
01:25:20,782 --> 01:25:22,784
Lumfong !
Lumfong!

786
01:26:15,045 --> 01:26:16,880
丹尼斯!
Denise!

787
01:26:19,466 --> 01:26:22,427
给我。来吧。我们走吧。
Give me that. Come on. Let's get out of here.

788
01:26:26,640 --> 01:26:28,642
来吧。
Come on.

789
01:26:38,860 --> 01:26:40,862
快点。来吧。
Hurry up. Come on.

790
01:26:51,873 --> 01:26:53,166
来吧。
Come on.

791
01:26:54,543 --> 01:26:56,503
我们走吧。
Let's go.

792
01:27:33,415 --> 01:27:36,501
这证实了我们最担心的事情。
This confirms our worst fears.

793
01:27:36,585 --> 01:27:39,004
原子反应是明确无误的。
The atomic reaction is unmistakable.

794
01:27:39,087 --> 01:27:41,006
我不明白。
I don't get it.

795
01:27:41,089 --> 01:27:44,426
我是说，我不明白为什么那个炸弹客会出现在跑道上。
I mean, I can't figure out why that bomber was on the runway.

796
01:27:44,509 --> 01:27:48,388
一架b-29在红色的空军基地做什么?
What would a b-29 be doin' on a red air base?

797
01:27:49,389 --> 01:27:51,391
这根本说不通。
It just doesn't make sense.

798
01:27:52,559 --> 01:27:56,831
对了，你不是告诉我我们在另一个岛上抓到的那个红色军官是空军吗?
Say, didn't you tell me that that red officer we picked up on the other island was in the air force?

799
01:27:56,855 --> 01:27:58,064
是的。一个主要的。
Yes. A major.

800
01:27:58,148 --> 01:28:00,148
-你问过他吗?——不可能的。
- Were you ever able to question him? - Impossible.

801
01:28:00,192 --> 01:28:02,861
-我试过了，但他一句话也不说。——哦。
- I tried, but he would not say a word. - Oh.

802
01:28:02,944 --> 01:28:04,863
哦,谢谢。
Oh, thanks.

803
01:28:04,946 --> 01:28:07,115
你和那个中国囚犯chin Lee谈过了吗?
Hey, did you talk to that Chinese prisoner, chin Lee?

804
01:28:13,663 --> 01:28:15,665
他没有看见那个囚犯。
He has not seen the prisoner.

805
01:28:15,749 --> 01:28:18,543
犯人没有见过他。
The prisoner has not seen him.

806
01:28:18,627 --> 01:28:23,089
霍特，把便携麦克风挖出来放在鱼雷室里。
Holter, dig up that portable microphone and plant it in the torpedo room.

807
01:28:23,173 --> 01:28:26,551
那就把犯人关在里面。别让他看到麦克风。
Then get the prisoner and lock him in there. Make sure he doesn't see the microphone.

808
01:28:26,635 --> 01:28:28,553
——正确的。-拉他一把，斯基。
- Right. - Give him a hand, ski.

809
01:28:28,637 --> 01:28:31,223
来吧。我们穿些干衣服吧。我们有工作要做。
Come on. Let's get into some dry clothes. We got work to do.

810
01:28:31,306 --> 01:28:34,226
-你有计划?-我要搞清楚这到底是怎么回事。
- You have a plan? - I'm gonna find out what this is all about.

811
01:28:34,309 --> 01:28:36,937
加油，chin Lee。我们有份工作给你。我们走吧。
Come on, chin Lee. We got a job for you. Let's go.

812
01:28:40,440 --> 01:28:42,400
-你们都准备好了吗?——是的。
- You guys got everything set? - Yep.

813
01:28:42,484 --> 01:28:44,402
好吧。
Okay.

814
01:28:44,486 --> 01:28:47,781
你确定阿成·李完全明白他该说什么吗?
Now, you're sure chin Lee understands exactly what he's supposed to say, huh?

815
01:28:51,493 --> 01:28:54,913
-他说什么?-他说他愿意为你做任何事。
- What'd he say? - He says he would do anything for you.

816
01:28:59,334 --> 01:29:03,880
他想让你打他的脸让他看起来更真实。
He wants you to strike him in the face to make it look more real.

817
01:29:06,591 --> 01:29:09,511
霍尔特。
Holter.

818
01:29:10,679 --> 01:29:12,806
他想让你去做。
He wants you to do it.

819
01:29:13,849 --> 01:29:16,393
他说你这样做不会痛。
He says it will not hurt if you do it.

820
01:29:26,903 --> 01:29:29,656
你没事吧，孩子?你没事吧?
You all right, boy? You okay?

821
01:29:30,657 --> 01:29:35,161
他的意思是什么?
What's he sayin'?

822
01:29:36,204 --> 01:29:43,003
他说……犯人很聪明，一定是被愚弄了。
He says... The prisoner is very intelligent and must be fooled.

823
01:29:49,593 --> 01:29:52,929
他想让你打他…困难。
He wants you to hit him... harder.

824
01:30:00,729 --> 01:30:02,689
对不起,朋友。
I'm sorry, pal.

825
01:30:09,988 --> 01:30:12,240
好了，把他弄出来。我们走吧。
All right, get him out. Let's go.

826
01:30:19,289 --> 01:30:21,750
在这里。来吧。把他们。
Here. Come on. Take 'em.

827
01:31:53,800 --> 01:31:55,719
这是难以置信的。
This is incredible.

828
01:31:55,802 --> 01:31:58,263
这是怎么回事，船长?
What's it all about, skipper?

829
01:31:58,346 --> 01:32:01,349
这是有史以来最离奇的情节。
This is the screwball plot of all time.

830
01:32:01,433 --> 01:32:05,812
他们会在朝鲜或者满洲投下原子弹然后怪到我们头上。
They're gonna drop an atomic bomb on Korea or manchuria and blame it on us.

831
01:32:08,356 --> 01:32:11,568
他们将在明天黎明乘坐改造过的轰炸机起飞。
They're taking off tomorrow at dawn in that made-over bomber.

832
01:32:23,329 --> 01:32:25,373
他发现了他!
He found him out!

833
01:33:37,112 --> 01:33:41,241
让我有足够的地面，这样我就可以绕着
J“ let me have plenty ground so that I can hop around j“

834
01:33:41,324 --> 01:33:44,285
请不要把我关起来
j“ not fencing me in, please j“

835
01:33:44,369 --> 01:33:46,412
让我有个小房子
j“ let me have little house j“

836
01:33:46,496 --> 01:33:48,414
J“竹席制J”
j“ made of bamboo mat j“

837
01:33:48,498 --> 01:33:52,085
j "哦，请不要把我在的地方围起来"
j“ oh, please not putting fence around where I am at j“

838
01:33:52,168 --> 01:33:55,213
j“我需要很大的空间，这样我才能摇摆猫j”
j“ I'm needing lots of room so I can swinging cat j“

839
01:34:22,574 --> 01:34:24,576
现在听我说。
Now listen to me.

840
01:34:27,662 --> 01:34:30,582
我要一个人去岛上。
I'm shoving off for the island alone.

841
01:34:30,665 --> 01:34:34,502
我就停在这里，在洞口附近。
I'll park myself right here, around the mouth of this cave.

842
01:34:34,586 --> 01:34:40,758
你会潜到离跑道半英里的地方，就在这里，这样你就能看到我的信号了。
You'll submerge half a mile beyond the runway, right around here, so you'll be able to spot my signal.

843
01:34:40,842 --> 01:34:44,345
大量的燃料会让轰炸机飞得很低。
Now a heavy load of fuel's gonna bring that bomber out low.

844
01:34:44,429 --> 01:34:50,059
所以当我给你信号…两个短，两个长，两个短……那就意味着飞机要起飞了。
So when I give you the signal... Two short, two long, two short... That'll mean the plane's taking off.

845
01:34:50,143 --> 01:34:53,521
这样你就有足够的时间浮出水面开火。
That'll give you just time enough to surface and fire.

846
01:34:55,607 --> 01:34:58,359
我要每把枪都投入战斗。
I want every gun in action.

847
01:34:58,443 --> 01:35:00,820
这意味着每一个人。
That means everybody.

848
01:35:00,904 --> 01:35:04,616
那架飞机必须被击落。
That plane has to be knocked out of the sky.

849
01:35:04,699 --> 01:35:11,748
你一撞到它，就冲到底部，待在那里，因为当炸弹击中它的时候，一切都会失控。
Now the minute you hit it, crash dive to the bottom and stay there, because everything's gonna break loose when that bomber hits.

850
01:35:11,831 --> 01:35:15,168
北边尽头有个小海湾，就在这里。我就藏在那里。
There's a cove at the north end, right here. That's where I'll hide.

851
01:35:15,251 --> 01:35:17,851
明晚十点整，我给你三个短眼罩。
Tomorrow night at 10:00 sharp, I'll give you three short blinkers.

852
01:35:17,879 --> 01:35:19,797
接我。
Pick me up.

853
01:35:19,881 --> 01:35:24,052
如果我没出现，你就离开，回家。
If I don't show up, shove off, head for home.

854
01:35:25,470 --> 01:35:27,472
有什么问题吗?
Any questions?

855
01:35:28,765 --> 01:35:30,892
我禁止这种疯狂的行为。
I forbid this insanity.

856
01:35:30,975 --> 01:35:34,020
禁止你想做的一切，教授。那架飞机撑不过去了。
Forbid all you want to, professor. That plane is not gonna make it.

857
01:35:34,103 --> 01:35:40,318
带回我们的怀疑得到证实的可怕报告已经够可怕的了。
It is dreadful enough to bring back the terrifying report that our suspicions are confirmed.

858
01:35:40,401 --> 01:35:47,325
但我们不能承担起挑起战争的责任，不管我们感觉如何。
But we cannot take it upon ourselves to commit an act of war, no matter how we feel.

859
01:35:47,408 --> 01:35:49,869
我们是平民!
We are civilians!

860
01:35:49,953 --> 01:35:53,081
这次探险由我负责。
I am responsible for this expedition.

861
01:35:53,164 --> 01:35:56,209
我命令你把这艘潜艇带回东京!
I order you to take this submarine back to Tokyo!

862
01:35:56,292 --> 01:35:58,211
我不在乎你和你的探险。
I don't care about you and your expedition.

863
01:35:58,294 --> 01:36:01,190
外面有一架敌方轰炸机伪装成美国轰炸机的样子。
There's an enemy bomber out there made up to look like an American bomber.

864
01:36:01,214 --> 01:36:04,842
它会掉下史上最大的蛋，而我们要承担罪责。
It's gonna drop the biggest egg in history, and we're gonna take the rap for it.

865
01:36:04,926 --> 01:36:07,178
我不喜欢那样。
I don't like that.

866
01:36:07,262 --> 01:36:11,891
所以从现在开始，教授，这是我的远征。
So from now on, professor, this is my expedition.

867
01:36:24,529 --> 01:36:26,447
队长!
Skipper!

868
01:36:26,531 --> 01:36:28,449
船走了!
The boat's gone!

869
01:36:28,533 --> 01:36:30,702
——什么?-船不见了。蒙特尔了它。
- What? - The boat's gone. Montel took it.

870
01:36:30,785 --> 01:36:33,413
-那你为什么不阻止他?-我们没有机会。
- Well, why didn't you stop him? - We didn't get the chance.

871
01:36:33,496 --> 01:36:36,308
他和她在甲板上。在我们知道发生了什么之前，他已经在船上走了。
He was on deck with her. Before we knew what happened, he was in the boat and gone.

872
01:36:36,332 --> 01:36:38,251
-那个女孩在哪?-在桥上。
- Where's the girl? - On the bridge.

873
01:36:44,632 --> 01:36:46,718
请。他不想让你阻止他。
Please. He doesn't want you to stop him.

874
01:36:46,801 --> 01:36:49,220
你为什么不阻止他?你只要喊一声就行了。
Why didn't you stop him? All you had to do was yell.

875
01:36:49,304 --> 01:36:52,181
他知道你的计划。他会执行的。这是他的命令。
He knows your plan. He'll carry it out. That's his orders.

876
01:36:52,265 --> 01:36:54,726
这就是你们这些天才的问题所在……充满了伟大的想法。
That's the trouble with you geniuses... Full of big ideas.

877
01:36:54,809 --> 01:36:56,853
现在你把一切都搞砸了。
Now you're fouling up the whole works.

878
01:36:56,936 --> 01:37:00,231
-你知道那个岛上到处都是士兵。-他也知道
- You know that island's crawling with soldiers. - He knows that too.

879
01:37:00,315 --> 01:37:04,193
那你为什么让这么好的一个老家伙抄近路去墓地?
Then why'd you let a nice old guy like that take a shortcut to the cemetery?

880
01:37:04,277 --> 01:37:06,279
他不是普通的二流教授，你知道的。
He's no ordinary two-bit professor, you know.

881
01:37:06,362 --> 01:37:08,489
他是蒙特尔，他的领域里的顶尖人物。
He's montel, top man in his field.

882
01:37:08,573 --> 01:37:11,453
但他又老又无助……除了试管，他什么都不知道。
But he's old and helpless... doesn't know his way outside of a test tube.

883
01:37:11,534 --> 01:37:13,614
你应该知道的。你和他合作得够近了。
You oughta know that. You work close enough with him.

884
01:37:13,661 --> 01:37:15,580
-你是什么样的女人?——停止!
- What kind of a woman are you? - Stop!

885
01:37:15,663 --> 01:37:17,665
-你没有感觉吗?——停止!
- Haven't you got any feelings? - Stop!

886
01:37:17,749 --> 01:37:19,667
他是我的父亲。
He's my father.

887
01:37:21,461 --> 01:37:23,463
什么?
What?

888
01:37:24,922 --> 01:37:26,841
我的父亲。
My father.

889
01:37:28,176 --> 01:37:31,012
哦，对不起，丹尼斯。
Oh, I'm sorry, Denise.

890
01:37:31,095 --> 01:37:33,181
我很抱歉。原谅我。
I'm sorry. Forgive me.

891
01:37:33,264 --> 01:37:40,813
他说那是他要去的地方……不是你的。
He said it was his place to go... Not yours.

892
01:37:43,358 --> 01:37:45,360
我很抱歉。
I'm sorry.

893
01:37:54,744 --> 01:37:56,788
她真的很有胆量。
She's sure got a lot of guts.

894
01:37:56,871 --> 01:37:59,290
我唯一不明白的是为什么会有这么大的谜团?
Only thing I can't figure out is why the big mystery?

895
01:37:59,374 --> 01:38:01,501
她为什么不告诉我们他是她老爸?
Why didn't she let us know he's her old man?

896
01:38:01,584 --> 01:38:05,755
这就是有个名人父亲的代价。
Well, that's what you have to pay for having a famous father.

897
01:38:05,838 --> 01:38:08,341
她一生都在一个位置上。
She's been on a spot all her life.

898
01:38:08,424 --> 01:38:11,969
想自力更生，她做到了。
Wanted to make good on her own, and she did.

899
01:38:12,053 --> 01:38:14,389
他很自豪，因为她做到了。
And he was proud because she did.

900
01:38:23,147 --> 01:38:25,108
看到他了吗?
Any sign of him at all?

901
01:38:28,611 --> 01:38:31,406
不,还没有。
No, not yet.

902
01:38:35,993 --> 01:38:37,954
他就在这里。
There he is.

903
01:38:39,414 --> 01:38:41,416
这是他的信号。
And there's his signal.

904
01:38:43,835 --> 01:38:46,587
战斗表面!枪行动!范围!
Battle surface! Gun action! Down scope!

905
01:38:46,671 --> 01:38:48,589
-你最好下去。——请。
- You'd better get below. - Please.

906
01:38:48,673 --> 01:38:49,674
好吧。
Okay.

907
01:39:05,857 --> 01:39:08,192
好吧,滑雪。我们走吧。
All right, ski. Let's go.

908
01:39:11,779 --> 01:39:14,615
来吧,威利。乔托，上来。
Come on, Willie. Joto, get up here.

909
01:39:28,129 --> 01:39:30,131
快点起来。快点起来。
Hurry it up. Hurry it up.

910
01:39:36,679 --> 01:39:38,347
火!
Fire!

911
01:40:59,387 --> 01:41:01,013
你对吧?
You all right?

912
01:41:02,056 --> 01:41:04,725
——哦。-炸弹一定是在我们脚下爆炸了。
- Oh. - The bomb must have gone off under us.

913
01:41:04,809 --> 01:41:06,727
让她回到航线上。
Bring her back on course.

914
01:41:06,811 --> 01:41:08,729
带她到潜望镜深度。
